<DOC><DOCNO> ZF310-603-519 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 603 519.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Computer Reseller News  April 15 1991 n416 p88(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Ingram Micro inks exclusive pact with Microtech. (MicrotechInternational Inc.)andM;</TITLE><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Microtech International and Ingram Micro have signed a three-monthexclusive agreement whereby Ingram Micro will distribute theentire Microtech line of Macintosh peripherals and other products.andO;Ingram's Macintosh and Apple Division and Mass Storage Divisioneach signed the contract and will each take part in marketing theMicrotech line.andP;  Microtech officials say this is the firstdistribution agreement for the vendor, which has changed itsorganization and support structure to facilitate reseller channeldistribution.andP;  The vendor signed a one-year contract, with anexclusive first three months, as a test.andP;  Company officials saythat a six- or 12-month exclusive agreement would not provideenough freedom and flexibility.andP;  There are no plans currently toadd other distributors at the end of the three months.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Ingram Micro Inc. (Contracts)Microtech International Inc. (Contracts).andO;Topic:     Distribution AgreementsComputer RetailingDealers and Agents.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>